# lmru--returns--autotests
Source code for LMRU Returns project. Automatic tests for project

## Prerequisites

Make sure you have installed all the following prerequisites on your development machine:

- [Git](https://git-scm.com)
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org) (version 16 LTS or higher)
- [Playwright](https://playwright.com) playwright framework

## Service development lifecycle

- Implement new tests
- Add or adapt assertions
- Add or change the documentation as needed
- Open pull request. Target the project's `master` branch

## How to use
- choose test in test folder
- type npx playwright test <testname> --headed --project=chromium --workers=1 --retries=2
- currently works only clientReturn.spec.js

